{"_path":"/maps/_ai/applications/paper-writing","_dir":"applications","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"ML 论文写作","description":"机器学习学术论文写作指南，包括 LaTeX 工具、文献管理与可复现性实践。","original_path":"_ai/paper-writing.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"ml-论文写作-ml-paper-writing"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ML 论文写作 (ML Paper Writing)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"latex-与学术写作工具"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LaTeX 与学术写作工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Overleaf 是在线协作 LaTeX 编辑的事实标准，内置 ACL、NeurIPS、ICML、ICLR、arXiv 等会议期刊模板。2025 年出现的 PaperDebugger 将 AI 辅助写作引入 Overleaf，通过多 Agent 系统在编辑器内提供语言润色、结构建议、引用验证等功能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.overleaf.com/latex/templates","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Overleaf 模板库"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/html/2512.02589v1","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PaperDebugger 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"文献管理与引用"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文献管理与引用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zotero 是开源文献管理的首选，支持浏览器插件一键保存、DOI 自动解析、与 Overleaf 集成。BibTeX 是 LaTeX 原生支持的引用格式，使用 DOI 可确保引用准确性。Mendeley 提供跨平台同步和协作批注功能。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.zotero.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zotero 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://icml.cc/Conferences/2025/CallForPapers","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ICML 2025 投稿指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"可复现性与开源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可复现性与开源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ML 论文可复现性 checklist 包括：使用 Git 管理代码版本、记录超参数和随机种子、保存中间 checkpoint、提供 Docker 封装环境。顶级会议（ICML、NeurIPS）要求接受论文必须发布代码和数据。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2003.12206","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ML Reproducibility Checklist"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ml-retrospectives.github.io/writing-guide/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How to Write a Good ML Paper"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"latex-与学术写作工具","depth":2,"text":"LaTeX 与学术写作工具"},{"id":"文献管理与引用","depth":2,"text":"文献管理与引用"},{"id":"可复现性与开源","depth":2,"text":"可复现性与开源"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:applications:paper-writing.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/applications/paper-writing.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/applications/paper-writing","_extension":"md"}